{"tid":1818844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網購需謹慎,千其唔好貪心墮入平價陷阱 損失5K慘痛經歷分享！！！","createTime":"2020-01-10T09:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T12:10:09.000Z","uid":345306,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"57cac8ad74c09fd0d00e290735fd97865dde8ff4","tid":1818844,"uid":345306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"話說小弟前兩日喺Facebook瀏覽Marketplace，點知咁啱見到有個Post話「新年促銷活動，全新iPhone 11Pro Max 限量優惠」iPhone 11Pro Max 256GB 賣HK$5500，於是就突發奇想，咁平不如入手一部自用或轉賣出去賺差價都抵喔。一直抱住呢個心態，DM左個賣家，佢話系公司搞活動所以先咁優惠，先到先得，部機全新，未開封同激活，有單有保養，免運費，即日落單翌日寄到，30日使用期，有問題無條件退換。聽落幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。於是我繼續問佢的公司資料，佢同我講公司係澳門，系電子商務公司，仲俾埋地址我，上網一搵又真係有喔，之後就信左佢，加佢WhatsApp落單。<br />\n<br />\n  但我發覺WhatsApp嗰個人好似唔係同FB那個人，就覺得可能系佢同事之類，我就冇留意太多。但我落單前要求佢send iPhone盒後面嘅IMEI碼同Serial Number 想核對下將寄過來部iPhone會唔會A貨，佢就send左張模糊左IMEI碼同Serial Number嘅iPhone盒背部資料相俾我，要求我想要原圖就入左數先，我就信左佢入左數，之後聲稱會將資料send俾公司先，稍後send原圖過來。<br />\n<br />\n  我等左好耐未send過黎，我再睇翻之前Marketplace個post 消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，後來就唔再覆Message 或搵藉口迴避話賣左部機俾人，晏啲send第二部俾我，個post俾Facebook審查緊晏啲彈出來之類。後來就越來越懷疑自己係唔係被人呃錢。點知俾左錢第二日，佢依然冇send 圖同關於運送消息，Post 一樣唔見，WhatsApp 同Facebook Message DM佢唔覆，突然消失左。就系咁大嗱嗱5500蚊被人呃左，欲哭無淚，貪心害死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n之後我就去左警署報案，希望警方可以徹查，拉到D騙徒，唔好俾佢地逍遙法外。<br />\n<br />\n  我之所以開呢個Post<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其一</span></strong>系純粹分享親身經歷唔想再有人貪心再跌落呢D所謂<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「促銷」，「清貨」，「全新正版&hellip;」呃錢陷阱</span></strong>，如果真系中招，就要報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不好啞忍；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其二</span></strong>系想提醒各位網購一定要去有信譽，信得過嘅商店買野，若涉及過數郵寄嘅商品，一定要再三考慮同核實先過數，特別二手商城Facebook Marketplace同 Carousell，好多類似的商品和騙子，最好就揀D可以面交的賣家購買。世界上絕對唔可能有咁着數嘅野俾你攞，見到商品價錢便宜得好誇張就一定<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">唔好入手同信啦</span>。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其三</span></strong>就系想邀請有心嘅絲打巴打幫手睇下有冇可能根據我提供的資料起到D仆街嘅底攞多D料，讓佢地唔可以得寸進尺，無所遁形。最後都係點醒我自己不要貪心，貪便宜信呢D野，當買左個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>幫下手push 同share出去俾多D人知道，見到類似嘅Post幫手<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">舉報</span></strong>，唔好中計！！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下系我同賣家嘅Facebook Message 對話記錄：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BChjnF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BChjnF.jpg&h=33c5c314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8ZfQum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8ZfQum.jpg&h=d5b76fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UuPaun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UuPaun.jpg&h=6fea0493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s57X3Pn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs57X3Pn.jpg&h=4fdd5554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjQboPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjQboPo.jpg&h=ce6b73e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmxX3Po.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmxX3Po.jpg&h=16aaf73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sxQEnK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sxQEnK.jpg&h=67eabcd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwVOq2K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwVOq2K.jpg&h=4bff74e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係我同賣家嘅WhatsApp對話記錄及附件：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OPrJZoi.jpg\" dat